{"arkId":"cl010111899","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010111899","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Bo\u00eete : Histoire de Diane","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Bo\u00eete : Histoire de Diane"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : \u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime (Occident)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1600 - 1650","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1600,"endYear":1650,"imprecision":"","text":"1ere moiti\u00e9 du XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Anonyme","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q4233718"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"CL 20824","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"accessoire personnel, bo\u00eete, \u00e9tui","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"L\u0027oeuvre est constitu\u00e9e d\u0027une bo\u00eete en \u00e9caille de tortue habill\u00e9e d\u0027un cylindre en ivoire ajour\u00e9. Deux moulures en ivorie tourn\u00e9 maintiennent ces \u00e9l\u00e9ments ensemble. Un couvercle, \u00e9galement tourn\u00e9 mais qui semble incomplet, s\u0027embo\u00eete. Ce couvercle, qui para\u00eet pertinent, \u00e9tait dissoci\u00e9 de la bo\u00eete ; elle en portait un autre en ivoire sculpt\u00e9 mais qui ne rentre pas dans l\u0027ouverture. Aucun de ces couvercles ne correspond \u00e0 celui qui se visse et qui est d\u00e9crit dans l\u0027inventaire imprim\u00e9 de la collection Rothschild \u00e0 Francfort. Sur le second couvercle en ivoire, au centre, deux amours aupr\u00e8s d\u0027un pi\u00e9destal portent un coeur br\u00fblant. Ils sont encadr\u00e9s d\u0027une torsade et d\u0027une frise d\u0027animaux et de chasseurs repr\u00e9sent\u00e9s sans souci d\u0027\u00e9chelle. Le relief en ivoire d\u00e9coup\u00e9 \u00e0 jour illustre deux \u00e9pisodes de l\u0027histoire de Diane : d\u0027un c\u00f4t\u00e9, la d\u00e9esse au bain, surprise par Act\u00e9on, l\u0027asperge d\u0027eau et le transforme en cerf. De l\u0027autre, elle surprend la grossesse de l\u0027une de ses compagnes, Callisto. La sc\u00e8ne se d\u00e9roule pr\u00e8s d\u0027une fontaine qui porte une figure \u00e0 cheval sur un globe ou un tonneau.","inscriptions":"Etiquette : \r ; N\u00b0146","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"9,3","displayDimension":"9,3 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Hauteur","value":"8,5","displayDimension":"8,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : ivoire d\u0027\u00e9l\u00e9phant = d\u00e9fense d\u0027\u00e9l\u00e9phant\r\nMat\u00e9riau : \u00e9caille de tortue","placeOfCreation":"Allemagne (Europe)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Francfort, collection Mayer von Rothschild ; Paris, collection Ad\u00e8le de Rothschild ; legs Baronne Salomon de Rothschild, 1922","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Rothschild, Baronne Salomon de, n\u00e9e Ad\u00e8le de Rothschild","note":"","role":", Collectionneur ; Donateur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"legs","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date du legs","value":"1922","startYear":1922,"endYear":1922}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e national du Moyen-\u00c2ge - mus\u00e9e de Cluny, Paris","longTermLoanTo":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"legs"}